## Git Discipline

- **Small commits** — one logical change each.
- **Meaningful messages** — imperative mood, complete sentences, explain *why*:

  ```
  Add onboarding answer persistence for M2

  Stores required interview responses in Supabase so later milestones
  can generate the Career Graph from real data, per onboarding-intelligence.md.
  ```

- **Never leave the repository broken** — lint, typecheck, and local dev must pass before ending work.
- No secrets in commits. Document env vars in `.env.example`.
- **Only commit when the user explicitly requests it.**

